Moshoeshoe Chabeli (nwụrụ n'ọnwa Ọktoba 30, 2013) bụ onye na-eme ihe nkiri na South Africa.

O gosipụtara Harold na ihe nkiri 2003, Stander na Thomas Jane.  O gosikwara onye ụkọchukwu na ihe nkiri 2013, The Forgotten Kingdom  Na telivishọn ọ pụtara na sitcom, Mponeng, nke bụ South African adaptation nke British sitcom, Keeping Up Appearances.
Ọ bụ nwa eze nke Moshoeshoe I
Ọ nwụrụ n'ụbọchị iri atọ n'ọnwa Ọktoba n'afọ 2013 mgbe ọ lụsịrị ọrịa kansa.
